samuel james \ `` sam \ '' cassell , retired american professional basketball player assistant coach washington wizards . 
6 ft 3 , 185 lb 84 kg ; 13.2 st point guard select florida state university houston rockets 24th overall pick 1993 nba draft . 
win two nba championships first two season league member rockets , third boston celtics 2008 . 
vote nba all-star game all-nba team , 2003-04 season . 
play phoenix suns , dallas mavericks , new jersey net , milwaukee bucks , minnesota timberwolves , boston celtics , sacramento kings los angeles clippers . 
